sentence: Among the underlying components of the Russell 3000 index, we saw noteworthy options trading volume today in Home Depot Inc (Symbol: HD), where a total of 19,561 contracts have traded so far, representing approximately 2.0 million underlying shares.
That amounts to about 44.5% of HD's average daily trading volume over the past month of 4.4 million shares.
Especially high volume was seen for the $220 strike call option expiring August 30, 2019, with 952 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 95,200 underlying shares of HD.

Especially high volume was seen for the $49 strike call option expiring September 06, 2019, with 3,183 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 318,300 underlying shares of ATVI.
